694	# Envoy fails to load AI plugins and forwards requests to upstream LLMs
695	# without Host header rewrite, resulting in 404s from the LLM backend.
696	# The base higress/all-in-one image normally runs this as a separate
697	# `plugin-server` supervisord program with its own nginx instance, but
